Package com.b2international.commons.dynamic

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    DynamicList
    Represents an immutable list that associates non-negative integer indexes with DynamicValues.
    DynamicMap
    Represents an immutable map that associates Strings with DynamicValues.
    DynamicMap.Entry
    Stores mapped property-value pairs.
    DynamicValue
    Encapsulates an object of indeterminate type.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractDynamicMap  
    AbstractDynamicMap.EntryImpl  
    AbstractDynamicValue
    Abstract implementation of DynamicValue that handles AbstractDynamicValue.as(Class) and AbstractDynamicValue.as(Class, Object) methods and offers reasonable defaults for the rest of the interface.
    DynamicListImpl  
    DynamicMapImpl  
    DynamicValueImpl
    An implementation of DynamicValue that captures a single Object.
